(4, 1, 21, 'Yaiba, Manga Karya Gosho Aoyama Siap Diadaptasi jadi Anime', '/storage/foto_berita/foto_1715611077.jpg', 'Manga karya Gosho Aoyama berjudul Yaiba', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">TIMESINDONESIA, JAKARTA</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">&nbsp;– Beberapa waktu lalu&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://timesindonesia.co.id/tag/Gosho-Aoyama\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">Gosho Aoyama</a><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">sudah pamit untuk rehat membuat manga&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://timesindonesia.co.id/tag/Detective-Conan\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">Detective Conan</a><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">. Rupanya dibalik rehatnya itu ia sekalian mempersiapkan anime baru berjudul&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://timesindonesia.co.id/tag/Yaiba\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">Yaiba</a><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--bs-body-color); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Shonen Jump edisi 24 menuliskan Gosho akan menjadi pengawasnya selama proses produksi.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">Diketahui, Yaiba manga karya Gosho Aoyama. Mangaitu pertama kali dipublis tahun 1988 hingga 1993. Manga itu kemudian merajai pasar komik di seluruh dunia. Di Indonesia Yaiba diterbitkan melalui Elex Media Komputindo pada 2004.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">Yaiba nggak kalah populer dengan Detective Conan dengan meraih Shogakukan Manga Award tahun 1993.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--bs-body-color); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Gosho Aoyama terinspirasi dari seorang pendekar pedang bernama Miyamoto Musashi. Ia merupakan seorang pendekar pedang asal Jepang yang amat terkenal.</span></p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; width: 697.99px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5153860653348599\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; background-color: transparent; height: 0px;\"><div id=\"aswift_6_host\" style=\"border: none; height: 0px; width: 698px; margin: 0px; padding: 