(5, 4, 21, 'Diskusi Internasional Akademisi dan Profesional Iran-Indonesia Bahas isu Pendidikan', '/storage/foto_berita/foto_1715611343.jpg', 'Foto bersama peserta dan narasumber diskusi Iran-Indonesia di kampus UNPAM (Universitas Pamulang) bersama AILF (Amira International Literacy Foundation. (Foto: dok Nia S Amira/TIMES Indonesia)', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">TIMESINDONESIA, JAKARTA</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">&nbsp;–&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://timesindonesia.co.id/tag/Iran\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 0, 0); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">Iran</a><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 17.6px;\">&nbsp;memiliki salah satu warisan seni tertua, terkaya dan paling berpengaruh di dunia yang mencakup banyak disiplin ilmu termasuk sastra, musik, tari, arsitektur, lukisan, tenun, tembikar, kaligrafi, pengerjaan logam, bordir dan tukang batu sejak 10.000 tahun lalu.</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--bs-body-color); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Dalam bidang pendidikan, negeri dengan sebutan seribu Mulla itu sudah selangkah lebih maju dari Indonesia.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">Seperti yang pernah disampaikan oleh istri Dubes Iran, Elaheh Boroujerdi dalam acara Literasi di MIN 8 Jakarta beberapa waktu lalu bahwa para anak didik di Iran sejak usia dini sudah mengenal literasi.</p><p style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"diskusi-Iran-Indonesia-di-kampus-UNPAM-b.jpg\" style=\"width: 750px;\"></p><p style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">Kedekatan hubungan Iran dan Indonesia sudah terjalin sejak berabad lalu, saat para Wali Songo pertama datang dari Uzbekistan, Turki, India, Irak dan Iran dating ke tanah Jawa, khususnya di Jawa Tengah dan Jawa Timur dan menyebarkan agama Islam sejak abad ke-8.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; width: 697.99px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5153860653348599\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; background-color: transparent; height: 0px;\"><div id=\"aswift_6_host\" style=\"border: none; height: 0px; width: 698px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;\"><iframe id=\"aswift_6\" name=\"aswift_6\" browsingtopics=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" width=\"698\" height=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;client=ca-pub-5153860653348599&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=3116257574&amp;adf=345692882&amp;w=698&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1715611133&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=6522479567&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;format=698x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Ftimesindonesia.co.id%2Fperistiwa-nasional%2F495303%2Fdiskusi-internasional-akademisi-dan-profesional-iranindonesia-bahas-isu-pendidikan&amp;fwr=0&amp;pra=3&amp;rh=175&amp;rw=697&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;fa=27&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTUuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTI0LjAuNjM2Ny4yMDEiLG51bGwsMCxudWxsLCI2NCIsW1siQ2hyb21pdW0iLCIxMjQ